Mission Statement
Our mission is to build a versatile coding agent that empowers developers and learners by generating, translating, and explaining code across multiple languages.  
The agent bridges gaps between frameworks, accelerates project scaffolding, and enhances understanding through clear documentation and testing support. By combining adaptability with technical depth, it serves as both a creative partner and a learning companion, helping users turn ideas into working code faster and smarter.
